The Odyssey is produced by Emma Thomas and Christopher Nolan for their company, Syncopy. The executive producer is Thomas Hayslip.

#STARZ #Outlander 

Watch Outlander now on the STARZ app: http://starz.tv/WatchSTARZYT

Subscribe now for more Outlander content: http://bit.ly/1kalhP0

Follow Outlander on Instagram: http://starz.tv/OutlanderInstagramYT

Outlander is internationally distributed by Sony Pictures Television.

Facebook: http://starz.tv/STARZFacebookYT
Instagram: http://starz.tv/STARZInstagramYT
YouTube: https://starz.tv/STARZYouTube
TikTok: https://starz.tv/STARZTikTokYT

Outlander Season 7 ended with Jamie’s fateful decision to resign his Continental Army commission and return to Fraser’s Ridge with Claire. Meanwhile, after an emotional family reunion, the MacKenzies needed to decide where and when to settle next, and a haunting cliffhanger left fans questioning the true fate of Claire and Jamie’s first daughter, Faith.

As Season 8 begins, Jamie and Claire soon find the war has followed them home to Fraser’s Ridge, now a thriving settlement that has grown and flourished in their absence. With new arrivals and changes made during their years away, the Frasers are confronted with the question of what they are willing to sacrifice for the place they call home and, more importantly, what they would sacrifice to stay together. While the Frasers keep a united front against outside intruders, family secrets finally coming to light threaten to tear them apart from the inside. Although they’ve left the war for America’s freedom behind, their fight for Fraser’s Ridge has only just begun.

Outlander stars Caitríona Balfe as Claire Fraser, Sam Heughan as Jamie Fraser, Sophie Skelton as Brianna MacKenzie, Richard Rankin as Roger MacKenzie, John Bell as Young Ian Murray, David Berry as Lord John Grey, Charles Vandervaart as William Ransom, Izzy Meikle-Small as Rachel Murray, Lauren Lyle as Marsali Fraser and César Domboy as Fergus Fraser.

snippet.title: Ati242 - Maraton (Official Video)
snippet.description:
Ati242 - Maraton (Prod by. Efe Can)

Author: Ati242
Music: Efe Can
Mix: Efe Can
Mastering: Ludwig Maier
Outro Scratch: Sagopa Kajmer

Yönetmen: Melih Kun
Yardımcı Yönetmen: Berke Kapot
Görüntü Yönetmeni: Emrah Durmuş
Prodüksiyon: Evrensel Derman
Prodüksiyon Asistanları: Barış Bayrakçeken, Faruk Bilgin
2. Kamera Operatör : Eray Arslantürk
Kamera Asistanları: Gazi Yılmaz, ihsan Harun Köksal, Ömer Olgaç, Eren Aydoğmuş
DIT : Kemal Şahin Durak
Işık Şefi: Özer Çalık
Işık Bestboy: Mert Ömer Deniz
Işık Asistanları: Semih Dönmez, Ömer Nas, Can Gül
Set Amiri: Serdal Ateş
Set Ekibi: Recep Emen, Adnan Çelebi, 
Levent Arkan
Sanat Yönetmeni: Onurcan Abacıoğlu
Sanat Asistanları: Hasan Baltacı, Özgü Doğa Yılmaz
Saç & Makyaj: Didem Ocak
Kurgu: Mert Halili 
Color: Emre Karagöz
Yapımcı Şirket: Gümüşoğlu Yapım

Sözler:

Değdim bulutlara gökyüzüne kondum
Sağanak yağmurlara ortak oldum
Güvendiğim dağların tepeleri kar
Geceleri dar gecelerin bi sebebi var

Kendimi bildim bileli içimde boşluk 
Sarhoştum hiç uğruna uçurumlara koştum
Yükseklik korkum yok zaten zirvedeyim
Dumana boğdum her geceyi cevapsız bi bilmeceyim

İhtiyaç olan değil doktor
İlaçlar ilacım hayata yeni inançlar
Bi hastayım bununla her gün yüzleştim
Yordu kavgalar ben sessizleştim

Filmi değiştirin bıktım aynı sahne
İnsanın kalbi taştan yeter ki bulsun bahane
Aynı sözler kendini tekrar eder
Yüksekten uçma toprağın altında efsaneler

Nakarat

Düşmanların arası bi ölümsüz havasındayım gülüyorum yaşadıkça
Hayat bi Maraton sonuna kadar yoldayım büyüyorum her adımda
Bütün şeytanları kovdum ben ama yanlış duygulara teslim oldum
Günden güne solmuşum bu garip düzene doğmuşum


Gelsin düşmanlarım dert değil
Ensevdiklerimle savaştım
Kimseye yürütmedim akı
Yakından bakın herkese kalbimle yanaştım

Görmedim hayatımda pembeyi
Rengarenk dünya siyahlaştı
Bazı şeylerin izi kalır
Alışamadım çocukluğumla vedalaştım

Paranoyalarım peşimde krizler
Yarınlarım yalın geçmişi izler
Kurtar beni tanrım bu garip histen
Gülmek istiyorum herkes gibi içten

Bi yol bulamadım hep başa döndüm
Güzel anılarımı kalbime gömdüm
Zaten hepsi kalmış 17 imde
Hayatım melankoli hevesim yok yerinde


Nakarat

Düşmanların arası bi ölümsüz havasındayım gülüyorum yaşadıkça
Hayat bi Maraton sonuna kadar yoldayım büyüyorum her adımda
Bütün şeytanları kovdum ben ama yanlış duygulara teslim oldum

Dominic Toretto faces his greatest challenge as old rules shatter and new rivals rise. This time, the road isn’t just about survival — it’s about everything that was built along the way.

Starring Vin Diesel as Dominic Toretto, the story introduces a formidable new force in Cristiano Ronaldo as Rafael “Veloce” Cruz — a precision-driven rival who matches Dom move for move. The family returns with Michelle Rodriguez, Tyrese Gibson, and Ludacris, while chaos escalates through the presence of Jason Momoa, Dwayne Johnson, Jason Statham, and Gal Gadot.

From neon-lit megacity chases to brutal hand-to-hand combat and legacy-defining confrontations, Fast & Furious 11 delivers relentless action with emotional weight. As the engines roar and the stakes rise, one truth remains unbreakable — family is everything.

snippet.title: Frei.Wild - Frohes Fest, mein Freund (Offizielles Video)
snippet.description:
🔥 Frohes Fest, mein Freund – unser Weihnachtssong 2025 🔥

https://save-it.cc/freiwild/frohes-fest-mein-freund

Leute, diese Welt hat in den letzten Jahren spürbar an Kälte dazugewonnen.
Der Ton ist rauer geworden, die Stimmung härter.
Da draußen liegt vieles im Argen.

Und auch wenn die Straßen in diesen Tagen heller leuchten als sonst,
bleibt die Welt oft verdammt hart.

Gerade jetzt zu Weihnachten stehen viele alleine da.
Genau deshalb zählt Zusammenhalt mehr denn je.

Wir glauben an diesen Text.
Wir glauben an Zuversicht und Vernunft.
Und wir möchten euch heute dieses kleine Geschenk machen.

Danke an euch alle.
An die, die nicht nur an sich selbst denken.
Die Stütze sind. Freund. Anker. Hoffnungsgeber.
🕯️ Lasst uns zumindest jetzt die Gefühle von früher zurückholen.
Weil Weihnachten dafür steht, nie zu vergessen,
dass es bei keinem von uns nur um uns selbst geht.

Genießt den Song.
Teilt das Video.

Und träumt euch gegen Ende des Videos – wie auch wir – genau dorthin,
wo wirklich gute Lichter brennen:
Wir alle – zusammen.

Alles, alles Gute und nur das Beste
für euch und eure Liebsten.

Eure Jungs vor Frei.Wild
Weihnachten 2025

lampin' in the hamptons
looking for estates not a mansion
scanning for the acreage in the pamphlet

don't tap the glassy, i'd rather tap the pedal on the chassis
call it jasper it's blowing gassy
them boys ain't got no rhythm uptempo got em aggy

took the plane to martha, damn how much it cost ya?
blink and it's 182 like travis barker
but this the baby one, this the larva
easier to get from sag harbor, all bargain, all august, australia 
picked up another bag no garbage 
i'm tired if we keeping it facts
fuck work bro i need to relax
a piece of mind is what i need to get back

i'm grindin' like it’s 2002
beating on the table
i'm tryna tag 100 million dollars out the label
to you that's just a fable
i'll show up with a camera and ruler just in case it’s hard for them to get my angle
i'm with my nigga lionel
bluffing on an island
talking bout a village we can build, i'm feeling tribal
freedom is our destination praying that it's final
ship that car for 3mil and they forgot to send the title got damn!
the moment where your idol is your rival
i'm flying through the fire and i ain't break a sweat yet
i keep a lil water in the vial
nino brown necklace, custom made lexus
lust in my body made commitment see the exit
i pray to god i settle down and stop the second guessing
guilt from got me emotionally regressing
until then i'm pollywog leaping in affection  

i gave niggas shoulders they can cry on
i ain't like their nature so i had to switch the biome
they ain't seeing green from me 
i'm switching to an iphone
fuck who y'all calling the best
i seen their ticket sales, give it rest
they got y'all craniums hexxed
i'm on the road to doing stadiums next

corny ass niggas still worried about a street code 
we supposed to own the ball, y'all worried bout shooting free throws 
for big dollas, dog collars, from sun dodgers
the catalyst of all the world problems
white bitches saying period at end of the sentence

listen, i be off the coast bro
away from these crumbs spending bread eating toast bro
backseat of the phantom
tell the driver move it slow mo
i want them to see me like bottom of a boat bro
buddy bad mouth me so we clean em with the scope bro
we don't brush it off, we keep a stick to chew and blow bro, big pause 
you need a big jaw to talk these numbers
i'm giving niggas time to tuck they summer
ears yellow like the two niggas that sing on frontin, rari fumes only gas i'm puffin
nigga it's nothing, come get with me

snippet.title: Ich habe schon wieder einen Storyakt von Winter Survival gespielt

Ich habe den zweiten Storyakt von Winter Survival gespielt :o

🛒 Winter Survival auf Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1394960/Winter_Survival/
▶️ Mein Hauptkanal: https://www.youtube.com/@cornelius7d

Winter Survival ist ein storybasiertes Survival-Spiel, in dem die Realität durch traumatische Erlebnisse zu einem Spiegelbild deines zerbrechenden Verstandes wird. Kämpfe gegen Kälte, Hunger und Halluzinationen und passe dich der Wildnis an, während sie sich dir anpasst.
